## Summary of Key Specs for US-025

| Property | ButtonPrimary | ButtonSecondary |
|---|---|---|
| **Background** | `--cta` (#F97316) | transparent |
| **Text color** | `--ink` (#0F172A) | `--ink` (#0F172A) |
| **Border** | none (solid bg) | 2px `--ink` border |
| **Corner radius** | 10px (token: `radii.button`) | 10px |
| **Typography** | `textStyles.body` (15px Rubik) | `textStyles.body` |
| **Shadow (normal)** | `shadows.hard` (offset 3,3) | `shadows.hard` (optional; design unclear) |
| **Shadow (pressed)** | `shadows.none` (offset 0,0) via SPRING_SOFT | `shadows.none` via SPRING_SOFT |
| **Scale on press** | 0.97 (SPRING_SOFT, damping 20, stiffness 180) | 0.97 |
| **Haptic** | Light on press | Light on press |
| **Disabled (both)** | grayed text (ink40), no shadow, haptic disabled | grayed text (ink40), no shadow, haptic disabled |
| **Loading** | spinner inline, input read-only | (not specified) |

**Press animation:** Reanimated `useSharedValue` + `useAnimatedStyle` with `withSpring(SPRING_SOFT, useReducedMotion())`. Collapse shadow from (3,3) → (0,0), scale 1 → 0.97.
